{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"14":"Fasting (Kitab Al-Siyam)"},"section_detail":{"14":{"hadithnumber_first":2313,"hadithnumber_last":2476,"arabicnumber_first":2313,"arabicnumber_last":2476}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2382,"arabicnumber":2382,"text":"حدثنا مسدد، حدثنا ابو معاوية، عن الاعمش، عن ابراهيم، عن الاسود، وعلقمة، عن عايشة، قالت كان رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم يقبل وهو صايم ويباشر وهو صايم ولكنه كان املك لاربه","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (1927) Sahih Muslim (1106)"}],"reference":{"book":14,"hadith":70}}]}